      <a href="images\ronin\chestplate.jpg">
      <img border="0" src="images/ronin/chestplate.jpg" align="right" width="91" height="191"></a>
      The Ronin carries a significant amount of weaponry.&nbsp; Much of it is
      self contained either in the torso or the gauntlets.&nbsp; Here we see the
      left chest plate that acts as protection for one of&nbsp; the internal
      weapons clusters.<br>
