  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left">
      <a href="images/ronin/openchest.jpg">
      <img border="0" src="images/ronin/small/openchest_small.jpg" align="right" width="100" height="77">
      </a> Seen here with the chest plates open, the Ronin shows off it's port and
      starboard weapon clusters.&nbsp; Each cluster consists of two type 4 PAC's
      (Particle Accelerator Cannon) and a single type 4 Graser. Such a
      combination of mass and heat gives the the Ronin the largest internal
      loadout in the history of the 'Corps.<br>
      <font color="#C0C0C0">
     (click thumbnail to view image)</td>
