    <td valign="top" align="left"> 
      <a href="images/ronin/elbow.jpg"> 
      <img border="0" src="images/ronin/small/elbow_small.jpg" align="right" width="100" height="116"> 
      </a> All of the joints on the Ronin were engineered for maximum
      range-of-motion.&nbsp; Seen here is the right elbow.&nbsp; Notice that,
      unlike human joints, this elbow can allow for 360 degrees of
      movement.&nbsp; This offers the pilot some unique tactical opportunities.<br>
      <font color="#C0C0C0">
     (click thumbnail to view image)</td>
