  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left">
      <a href="images/ronin/elbows.jpg">
      <img border="0" src="images/ronin/small/elbows_small.jpg" align="right" width="100" height="30">
      </a> The Ronin carries significant defensive capability as well.&nbsp; Each
      forearm carries ECM pods as well as proximity detection systems.&nbsp; Also visible here are the elbow joints and the primary exhaust filter.<br>
      <font color="#C0C0C0">
     (click thumbnail to view image)</td>
  </tr>
