    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left"><a href="images/ronin/left4arm.jpg"><img border="0" src="images/ronin/small/left4arm_small.jpg" align="right" width="100" height="122"></a>Designers of the Ronin had to
      expect their design to be involved in close combat with enemy vehicles and
      mecha.&nbsp; Based on after action reports, previous mecha have lacked a
      serious weapons system for close-quarters action.&nbsp; With this in mind,
      Johann Maus engineers incorporated the Pendeltaun Contained Laser Weapons
      System or CLAWS.&nbsp; Essentially, CLAWS gives the Ronin an energy blade
      of pure laser energy.<br>
      <font color="#C0C0C0">
     (click thumbnail to view image)</td>
