    <td valign="top" align="left"><a href="images/ronin/waistgun.jpg"><img border="0" src="images/ronin/small/waistgun_small.jpg" align="right" width="100" height="100"></a>Under the right side of the torso,
      just above the waist is a small Type 2 PAC.&nbsp; Intended to be used to
