    <td valign="top" align="left"><a href="images/ronin/scale.jpg"><img border="0" src="images/ronin/small/scale_small.jpg" align="right" width="100" height="69"></a>The Ronin stand approximately
      thirty-six feet tall (36').&nbsp; This makes it the tallest mecha in the
      SpaceCorps inventory.&nbsp; By contrast, the Kodiak measures in at
      twenty-six feet. (26').&nbsp; This image also shows the significant amount
      of armor that surrounds the ankle and foot joints.<br>
      <font color="#C0C0C0">
     (click thumbnail to view image)</td>
