  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left"><a href="images/ronin/pistol2.jpg"><img border="0" src="images/ronin/small/pistol2_small.jpg" align="right" width="100" height="106"></a>The M375 accelerates it's shells
      using a laser acclerator that is &quot;steerable&quot;&nbsp; Able to
      achive nearly hypersonic speeds, this weapon's bullets have been found to
      penetrate armor up to 750mm thick.&nbsp; The steerable laser allows the
      Ronin to aim around corners and over hills, thus eliminating the need to
      expose itself to enemy fire early in a conflict.<br>
