    <td valign="top" align="left"><a href="images/ronin/ronintop.jpg"><img border="0" src="images/ronin/small/ronintop_small.jpg" align="right" width="100" height="44"></a>Johann Maus engineers looked at
      all aspects of the Ronin's design.&nbsp; Seen from above here, the thin
