    <td valign="top" align="left"><a href="images/ronin/sensorpods.jpg"><img border="0" src="images/ronin/small/sensorpods_small.jpg" align="right" width="100" height="140"></a>Perhaps the greatest innovation
      the Ronin sports is the inclusion of extended sensor pods. <br>
      Able to detect emissions on all wavelengths, the sensor pods give Ronin
